---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About" description="About Voice and Plausible Potentials Consulting DAO">
  <section class="about">
    <div class="about__container container container--prose">
      <header class="about__header">
        <h1 class="about__title">About Voice</h1>
        <p class="about__subtitle">Sovereignty-first publishing for the cooperative economy</p>
      </header>
      
      <div class="about__content prose">
        <p class="about__lead">
          Voice is the publishing platform for <strong>Plausible Potentials Consulting DAO</strong> 
          and the <strong>C3 Alliance</strong> (Cosmic Commons Communities Alliance).
        </p>
        
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We believe in building alternatives to extractive capitalism through cooperative 
          structures, blockchain governance, and sovereignty-first design. Voice exists to 
          share the insights, frameworks, and progress of this work with anyone interested 
          in cooperative futures.
        </p>
        
        <h2>What is Plausible Potentials?</h2>
        <p>
          Plausible Potentials Consulting DAO LLC is a blockchain technology development 
          agency focused on cooperative economics infrastructure. We specialize in:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Exit-to-Cooperative (E2C) business conversion strategies</li>
          <li>Tokenomics design for cooperative governance</li>
          <li>Smart contract development (Cardano, Midnight Network, Cosmos)</li>
          <li>Community Land Trust infrastructure</li>
          <li>Sovereignty-first system architecture</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>What is the C3 Alliance?</h2>
        <p>
          The C3 Alliance (Cosmic Commons Communities Alliance) is a network of 
          cooperatives, community land trusts, and sovereign communities building 
          shared infrastructure for the cooperative economy. The Alliance provides:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Governance frameworks for decentralized cooperation</li>
          <li>Shared technology infrastructure (blockchain, identity, coordination tools)</li>
          <li>Physical nodes (N3 Commons) combining renewable energy, food production, and community space</li>
          <li>Educational resources and community support</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Cyber-Mutualism</h2>
        <p>
          Our work is grounded in <strong>Cyber-Mutualism</strong> â€” a synthesis of 
          Spinozan philosophy, mutualist economics, and blockchain technology. This 
          framework guides our approach to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Coordination without coercion</li>
          <li>Value creation without extraction</li>
          <li>Governance without centralized authority</li>
          <li>Technology as a tool for liberation, not control</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For inquiries about Plausible Potentials services or C3 Alliance membership:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@plausiblepotentials.com">contact@plausiblepotentials.com</a></li>
          <li>Website: <a href="https://plausiblepotentials.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">plausiblepotentials.com</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <footer class="about__footer">
        <div class="about__signature">
          <span class="about__signature-name">Plausible Potentials</span>
          <span class="about__signature-title">Consulting DAO LLC</span>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0 var(--space-24);
  }
  
  .about__header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-8);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  .about__title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  
  .about__subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  
  .about__lead {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .about__content {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }
  
  .about__content h2 {
    color: var(--royal-blue);
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
  }
  
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .about__content h2 {
      color: var(--gold);
    }
  }
  
  .about__footer {
    padding-top: var(--space-8);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  .about__signature {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-1);
  }
  
  .about__signature-name {
    font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive;
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  
  .about__signature-title {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
</style>
